                  children:
                    "4. The mutated Magickian will now repeat step 8 yet let N’Aton replace the serpent, or take the shape of a Serpent of his likeness; and let the magickians spine be as the column of the cosmos, where N’Aton will be meeting the Forgotten Ones themselves as cosmic forces, transcending them to find TAT.",
